# ================== 统一换行符 / 文本文件 ==================
*.php   text eol=lf
*.sh    text eol=lf
*.md    text eol=lf
*.yml   text eol=lf
*.yaml  text eol=lf
*.json  text eol=lf
*.html  text eol=lf
*.css   text eol=lf
*.js    text eol=lf
*.txt   text eol=lf

# 让 Git 按文本方式处理这些文件，避免 Windows / Linux 来回切换出现 CRLF/LF 乱七八糟的问题
* text=auto

# ================== 二进制文件标记 ==================
97bot binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.zip binary
*.gz  binary
*.tar binary
